Program: Discovery
Title: Columbia Astronauts
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrynx
Last Broadcast Date: 14 May 2004
A report from Wyoming where the 2003 Columbia astronauts went on a wilderness expedition. The programme was recorded in the Wind River Mountain Range of Wyoming, where the seven Space Shuttle Columbia astronauts came to complete a wilderness expedition in the months before their fateful space mission. The crew died when the shuttle re-entered earth's atmosphere following an expedition in February 2003. Show less